  <Description>
    <Language>en</Language>
    <Type>General</Type>
    <Text>Mr. C Beverly Hills is a stylish 5-star hotel promising elegant accommodation and excellent facilities, in the south of Beverly Hills. Highlights include a swimming pool and Italian restaurant. Located in Beverly Hills, roughly 15km from the centre of Los Angeles, the hotel is a luxurious haven that offers a car rental service. Attractions include Rodeo Drive and Greystone. In nearby West Hollywood, guests can experience Sunset Strip, The Roxy Theatre and The Schindler House. The beaches of Santa Monica are also close by. The hotel occupies a charming mid-rise whose interior boasts stylish European glamour and dark hardwood floors. Facilities include an outdoor swimming pool, fitness centre, and spa offering a range of beauty and massage treatments. Free Wi-Fi is available throughout the premises. The hotel restaurant offers delicious Italian cuisine in a sophisticated setting. The bar serves a wide selection of hot and cold beverages. Deluxe City View rooms are 33sqm and beautifully-appointed, featuring Old World simplicity, vintage photography and a balcony. Amenities include a flat-screen satellite TV, mini-bar and en-suite bathroom with shower. Free parking is possible onsite.</Text>
